{"tid":886800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭被日媒問　香港會否變了另一個中國城市　林鄭依依哦哦","createTime":"2018-11-02T11:29:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T07:22:05.000Z","uid":47714,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ad9cf58a1b0b7c659955c878b136bb1ec577cf13","tid":886800,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:29:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181101/58862178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181101%2F58862178&d=TNc28JJvEqMuoJKdm3yFAkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=6dc0feae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181101%2F58862178&h=845dbe98\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181101/58862178</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181101/large/1541057231_7138.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181101%2Flarge%2F1541057231_7138.jpg&h=2ac2d80e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥連日出席貿發局在日本東京舉行的「Think Global, think HK」活動，在訪問環節中，日本傳媒四次發問，三度質疑香港自由社會包括新聞自由是否倒退，不少更是針對《金融時報》編輯馬凱簽證不獲續發有關，更有日本記者問香港回歸21年後，會否變了中國另一個城市。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥回答時指出，香港回歸中國已21年，一直奉行一國兩制，並形容這個制度是香港利益所在，香港亦奉行法治、自由等。她說：「喺你問題入面有講過香港自由是否倒退的顧慮，但呢樣要證據去證明，香港有過百個駐地記者，報道香港、中國、亞洲，已經係自由嘅證明。」<br />\n<br />\n被問到馬凱為甚麼不能續簽證，林鄭月娥指出，各國都有入境政策，個別案件不能續一評論，而該名人士亦已上訴，只能說香港政府是根據法律執行入境政策。<br />\n<br />\n回答最後一條關於香港自由倒退的問題時，林鄭指部份人對香港的主觀印象難以控制，但香港在全球調查上亦有良好排行，「你嚟香港做嘢感受下，並非好似其他報道或你聽到咁。」<br />\n<br />\n她又說除了是次記者發問外，是次外訪從未有其他在日本會面的人問過相關問題，「不過我歡迎發問。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有片　有冇巴絲識日語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://isd.wecast.hk/vod/?id=8884\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fisd.wecast.hk%2Fvod%2F%3Fid%3D8884&d=TNc28JJvEqMuoJKdm3yFAkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=b3229e80\" target=\"_blank\">https://isd.wecast.hk/vod/?id=8884</a>"},{"pid":"e6df1ec72aa64422c69dd914665d313c4baf51a4","tid":886800,"uid":203813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6744a527cb4735e08f411ffd1184f4f3046408f","tid":886800,"uid":191812,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:36:45.000Z","msg":"你嚟香港做嘢感受下，並非好似其他報道或你聽到咁,而係比你想像中差好多"},{"pid":"8c1b2c08779ee824166d8b8e7e9c487343e32285","tid":886800,"uid":41245,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:41:01.000Z","msg":"錄音機咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係嗰啲咩一國兩制，咩尊重言論自由嗰啲嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b289ca5688e077acef204669a731328fdef7abf","tid":886800,"uid":47160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錄音機咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係嗰啲咩一國兩制，咩尊重言論自由嗰啲嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢就係蠢到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b92623e9bc23ab6b7044d1efc289a8b755c88d4","tid":886800,"uid":38194,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:51:24.000Z","msg":"777閪婆令我諗起林瑞麟"},{"pid":"8ab79f76579cec70ee334adb91eee2967010866c","tid":886800,"uid":28155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b92623e9bc23ab6b7044d1efc289a8b755c88d4","tid":886800,"uid":38194,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:51:24.000Z","msg":"777閪婆令我諗起林瑞麟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:55:03.000Z","msg":"林狗仲好過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0801d03481f35e1288ca9ff385605a3720cd3c","tid":886800,"uid":92277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8c1b2c08779ee824166d8b8e7e9c4873